QuestData.Title: Work Order: Shado-Pan I
QuestData.Description: <Yoon's writing seems rushed. He must have been excited.>$b$bThe Shado-Pan want crops from you! What an honor indeed!$b$bA request came in this morning for green cabbages. Apparently, they make a rather tasty cabbage soup with them.$b$bOnly the finest will do for the Shado-Pan!
QuestData.LogDescription: Plant 8 Green Cabbage Seeds on Sunsong Ranch.
